================================================================================
ðŸ’¥ NEO BRUTAL STYLE GUIDE (Neobrutalism)
================================================================================

VISUAL LANGUAGE:
- **Form**: Bold, unapologetic, raw with thick borders and hard shadows
- **Colors**: High contrast black/white base, punchy accent colors (#f59e0b, #ef4444, #10b981), flat tones
- **Typography**: Bold sans-serif (Space Grotesk, Archivo Black) with thick weights, tight tracking
- **Shapes**: Sharp corners or minimal rounding (0.25rem), thick borders (2-4px), hard drop shadows
- **Interaction**: Instant feedback (no slow transitions), color inversions, position shifts

DESIGN TOKENS GUIDANCE:
- Background: White or bold color (#fef3c7, #fce7f3, #dbeafe) or pure black
- Primary: Vibrant solid colors (#f59e0b, #ef4444) with thick black borders
- Surface: White/colored cards with 3-4px black borders, hard offset shadows (4-8px solid black)
- Radius: 0.25rem (minimal) or 0 (sharp corners)
- Shadow: Hard drop shadows with no blur (e.g., 4px 4px 0 black)
- Animation: 100-200ms snap transitions, no easing (linear)

COMPONENT PATTERNS:
- Buttons: Thick black border, bold background color, hard shadow, invert on hover/press
- Cards: Solid border, offset hard shadow, no gradients, bold titles
- Inputs: Thick border, no inner shadow, solid focus state with color change
- Text: All caps for emphasis, bold weights, high contrast

LAYOUT & SPACING:
- Grid-based layouts with clear separation
- Bold section dividers (thick horizontal lines)
- Compact spacing with intentional density
- Background: Solid colors or bold patterns (dots, stripes), no gradients

ATMOSPHERE:
- Rebellious, confident, in-your-face
- Maximalist use of color and contrast
- Raw, unpolished intentionally
- Instant, snappy interactions

DO NOT:
- Use soft shadows or blurs
- Apply gradients or transparency
- Create rounded pill shapes
- Use subtle or muted colors

================================================================================

